Trans and Non-binary, 2SLGBTQ+ Climbing Sessions
scheduled_activities.description:
Trans and Non-binary & 2SLGBTQ+ programming aims to provide a safe, comfortable, inclusive, and fun atmosphere for the Trans and Non-binary & 2SLGBTQ+ community. Friends are welcome if participating with a member of the Trans and Non-binary & 2SLGBTQ+ community. Attendees can expect programming to be delivered and/or supervised by a members or allies of the aforementioned community. 

*A Climbing Membership or Day Pass is still required for these sessions.

scheduled_activities.description:
Take a break and enjoy the PAC pool under the supervision Lifeguards. Swim, play basketball or bounce off the diving board! Lanes are available for lengths and recreational swimming and the diving well is open during this time. The PAC Admissions Policy and Swim Tests apply to all swims. ** Please note there may be cancellations due to facility closures or other department bookings.
